text.text: Very ancient and Holi temple of godess Hulgamma Devi. It is a Hindu temple. Many people visit here in the month of May every year. Very crowded place during fastival. Road is available from station to temple but very few autos or buses are available. Frequency is very low of autorickshaw. During summer season temparature is very high.
